{
  "texts": [
    "-WizardCoder.",
    "WizardCoder [59] is a state-of-the-art LLM of code that enhances code generation and comprehension through advanced instruction fine-tuning techniques.",
    "It utilizes the Evol-Instruct [98] method that enables fine-tuning with more complex and diverse instructions for better code-related instruction following.",
    "We use WizardCoder-15B-V1.0 in this study to evaluate its applicability in federated learning.",
    "Mistral-7B [29] uses Mistral as the base model and has made progress in the attention mechanism, demonstrating the potential of auto-regressive models."
  ]
}